The paper deals with stochastic optimization problems in machine learning, which is a core topic in the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses convergence rates and algorithms for optimization, which are topics in numerical analysis (cs.NA). The use of local quadratic approximations of loss functions is a common technique in optimization and machine learning (cs.AI). The paper also involves analyzing and comparing experimental results, which is a common practice in data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses generalization error, which is a topic in statistical inference (cs.SI).
